1
00:00:00,376 --> 00:00:04,900
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:04,900 --> 00:00:10,404
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,404 --> 00:00:16,832
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,832 --> 00:00:21,312
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,312 --> 00:00:25,760
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:30,671
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,671 --> 00:00:34,720
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,720 --> 00:00:39,255
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,255 --> 00:00:43,552
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,552 --> 00:00:48,317
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,317 --> 00:00:51,808
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,808 --> 00:00:55,488
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,134 --> 00:01:00,512
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,512 --> 00:01:03,200
=Episode 28=

15
00:01:05,033 --> 00:01:09,166
I mean you need to
take good care of yourself.

16
00:01:09,366 --> 00:01:10,966
Anyway, don't push yourself so hard.

17
00:01:22,566 --> 00:01:23,900
What a coincidence.

18
00:01:33,233 --> 00:01:36,666
We'd better not stay here.
Shall we leave now?

19
00:01:37,300 --> 00:01:40,833
Sure, I can take you home.

20
00:01:47,366 --> 00:01:49,866
So it is you
who has been helping our Xi'er.

21
00:01:50,066 --> 00:01:51,433
I really appreciate it.

22
00:01:51,500 --> 00:01:53,433
May I ask your name?

23
00:01:53,566 --> 00:01:56,066
My name is Ling Feng.

24
00:01:56,066 --> 00:01:57,000
Oh.

25
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,833
- Everyone calls me Prince.
- Prince.

26
00:01:58,833 --> 00:02:00,966
- Yeah.
- Prince.

27
00:02:00,966 --> 00:02:02,433
Auntie, if you don't mind,

28
00:02:03,100 --> 00:02:04,100
you can call me son.

29
00:02:04,100 --> 00:02:06,666
You're kidding.

30
00:02:06,666 --> 00:02:08,100
- Have some tea.
- No, thanks.

31
00:02:08,100 --> 00:02:09,666
If you don't mind,

32
00:02:09,833 --> 00:02:11,133
I can call you mother.

33
00:02:11,566 --> 00:02:14,566
Did my daughter do
something to offend you?

34
00:02:14,566 --> 00:02:16,160
No.

35
00:02:16,700 --> 00:02:19,366
Your daughter has had
a crush on me for a long time.

36
00:02:19,366 --> 00:02:22,833
What? Isn't she in love with the Boss?

37
00:02:25,033 --> 00:02:27,566
It's just media hype,
and can't be trusted.

38
00:02:28,266 --> 00:02:29,433
- Then, Son.
- Yes.

39
00:02:29,433 --> 00:02:32,766
No, Prince.
Do you need something from me?

40
00:02:32,766 --> 00:02:34,433
Right.

41
00:02:34,700 --> 00:02:35,633
There's something

42
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:37,433
- I've been wanting to tell you.
- Okay.

43
00:02:37,433 --> 00:02:38,833
I'll just say it now.

44
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:40,466
What's it?

45
00:02:40,866 --> 00:02:44,500
Your daughter has had
a crush on me for a long time.

46
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:51,900
No, that's not it.

47
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:56,166
Here's the thing.

48
00:02:56,833 --> 00:02:59,333
Xi'er has accepted a job
as a boxing coach.

49
00:03:00,066 --> 00:03:01,500
She's going abroad next month.

50
00:03:01,900 --> 00:03:04,466
She just got back not long ago.
Why is she leaving again?

51
00:03:05,900 --> 00:03:07,366
She asked me not to tell you.

52
00:03:08,266 --> 00:03:10,233
But I've thought about it,

53
00:03:10,266 --> 00:03:11,833
and I think I should
discuss it with you.

54
00:03:12,133 --> 00:03:14,733
After all, I don't want her
to leave either.

55
00:03:33,500 --> 00:03:34,533
Xi'er is back.

56
00:03:36,500 --> 00:03:38,866
If she knew I came to see you,

57
00:03:40,300 --> 00:03:42,033
she would definitely break my legs.

58
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:44,866
Then hide now.

59
00:03:55,066 --> 00:03:57,133
Mother, why are you hiding?

60
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:59,133
I can't keep a secret.

61
00:03:59,300 --> 00:04:01,400
I'm afraid I'll give it away
if I get asked later.

62
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:04,433
Okay, I'm just feeling a bit bad.

63
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:06,700
Don't call me mother.

64
00:04:06,700 --> 00:04:08,000
Okay, mother.

65
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:12,288
Mother.

66
00:04:13,100 --> 00:04:15,566
Mother. Where's she?

67
00:04:22,866 --> 00:04:25,533
So this is where Heroine lives.

68
00:04:30,033 --> 00:04:32,166
Mr. Zeng, don't you have anything to do?

69
00:04:36,766 --> 00:04:41,233
Mr. Zeng, why don't we turn on the radio
and listen to some music?

70
00:04:42,233 --> 00:04:43,266
Okay.

71
00:04:50,766 --> 00:04:54,466
Mother, it's Xi'en. We can go out now.

72
00:04:54,766 --> 00:04:57,533
Wait, isn't her boyfriend

73
00:04:58,300 --> 00:04:59,566
Lan Chen?

74
00:05:00,633 --> 00:05:02,100
She likes Lan Chen too?

75
00:05:03,166 --> 00:05:05,533
Keep it down. Let me see.

76
00:05:11,633 --> 00:05:12,633
This is your house.

77
00:05:12,633 --> 00:05:15,930
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

78
00:05:19,168 --> 00:05:22,100
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

79
00:05:22,100 --> 00:05:26,466
Mr. Zeng, I see
you've been close to my sister recently.

80
00:05:27,066 --> 00:05:28,466
What's your relationship?

81
00:05:28,700 --> 00:05:31,700
We are friends. I just appreciate
your sister very much.

82
00:05:34,066 --> 00:05:37,333
By the way, Mr. Zeng,
how's our new plan?

83
00:05:37,900 --> 00:05:39,833
Your plan has a lot of problems.

84
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:44,433
Impossible. My sister,
Lan Chen and I all think it's good.

85
00:05:58,366 --> 00:06:01,200
That's not right. Lots of data
has been tampered with.

86
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:03,133
And a lot of selling points
have been deleted.

87
00:06:03,566 --> 00:06:04,700
It is a big problem.

88
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:07,166
May I ask who sent it to your company?

89
00:06:12,766 --> 00:06:16,233
Your project department sent it
to our marketing department manager.

90
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:18,700
As for who it was, I really don't know.

91
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:20,566
How about this?

92
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:22,300
I'll send you

93
00:06:22,500 --> 00:06:23,900
our real plan.

94
00:06:35,100 --> 00:06:36,433
It's Lan Chen and my sister.

95
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:40,166
Sorry, Mr. Zeng.
Can you hide for a moment?

96
00:06:40,333 --> 00:06:41,792
What?

97
00:06:42,066 --> 00:06:43,566
Lan Chen will get angry if he sees you.

98
00:06:44,033 --> 00:06:45,433
I don't need to hide, right?

99
00:06:46,033 --> 00:06:49,200
And you and your sister
can already tell Lan Chen about this.

100
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:51,133
There's no time to explain. Sorry.

101
00:06:55,666 --> 00:06:56,900
Mother, why are you here?

102
00:07:00,466 --> 00:07:02,900
No time to explain. Hide now.

103
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:06,233
Hurry up.

104
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:09,866
Why are you guys here?

105
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:16,866
Mother. Where's she?

106
00:07:23,866 --> 00:07:27,433
Lan Chen, don't you have anything to do?

107
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:36,466
Stop looking.
How about eating something?

108
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:40,288
Okay.

109
00:07:41,166 --> 00:07:42,566
Then I'll go get you something.

110
00:07:46,666 --> 00:07:47,966
You guys.

111
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:52,566
How can I...?

112
00:08:02,266 --> 00:08:06,100
Lan Chen, I'm tired.

113
00:08:06,700 --> 00:08:09,300
I want to rest. Why don't you go back?

114
00:08:11,066 --> 00:08:13,033
I'm tired too.

115
00:08:14,066 --> 00:08:16,766
May I have a rest in your room?

116
00:08:17,233 --> 00:08:19,166
What? What are you going to do?

117
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:24,133
What? Only you can rest in my room,

118
00:08:24,666 --> 00:08:25,933
and I can't rest in your room?

119
00:08:26,300 --> 00:08:27,633
Can it be the same for men and women?

120
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:34,666
Okay, I was just joking with you.

121
00:08:36,366 --> 00:08:39,266
But your bed can't hold

122
00:08:39,566 --> 00:08:42,266
a perfect man like me.

123
00:08:45,166 --> 00:08:46,100
I'm leaving.

124
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:51,233
Hurry up. It's going to rain soon.

125
00:08:52,566 --> 00:08:53,466
I'm really leaving.

126
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:57,433
(Everyone,
the touching music just ended.)

127
00:08:58,233 --> 00:09:01,466
(We'll play a confession message sent
to our Confidant Radio.)

128
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:04,566
(It's not my first time in love.)

129
00:09:06,466 --> 00:09:08,766
(But why can't I forget about you?)

130
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:14,133
(You narcissistic guy.)

131
00:09:18,566 --> 00:09:20,700
(You're really special to me,)

132
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,966
(but my sister also likes you.)

133
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:29,533
(I'm pretending to be my sister now.)

134
00:09:30,233 --> 00:09:31,766
(What can I do?)

135
00:09:33,500 --> 00:09:37,666
(I really fell in love
with you, Lan Chen.)

136
00:09:55,466 --> 00:09:56,866
How long are you going
to hide it from me?

137
00:09:57,533 --> 00:09:58,533
Miss Jin!

138
00:10:09,039 --> 00:10:13,561
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

139
00:10:16,591 --> 00:10:21,552
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

140
00:10:24,601 --> 00:10:30,425
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

141
00:10:30,425 --> 00:10:37,895
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

142
00:10:37,895 --> 00:10:41,376
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

143
00:10:41,376 --> 00:10:45,497
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

144
00:10:45,497 --> 00:10:47,193
♪Open my secret♪

145
00:10:47,193 --> 00:10:53,241
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

146
00:10:53,241 --> 00:10:57,113
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

147
00:10:57,113 --> 00:11:01,619
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

148
00:11:01,619 --> 00:11:10,329
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
